name: Coming Home
description:
It was 6 in the morning when I woke up at the hotel I stayed in Pelabuhan Ratu.

I walked to my room's balcony, sipped my morning coffee while contemplating such beautiful view. 

Life couldn't be better.

Not long before I knew I had to grab my camera, and snapped this photograph.

Of a fishermen boat moved slowly to the shore, coming home from the sea.

This is one of endless stunning views in Pelabuhan Ratu, West Java-Indonesia.

JPEG, 4x5 aspect ratio.
